OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and damp start to the
OL,6,Fday, with some patchy rain and
OL,7,Fdrizzle. A limited amount of
OL,8,Fbrightness developing during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, with coastal and hill fog
OL,10,Fpersisting around Cornwall and Devon.
OL,11,FWarmer than of late, but rather breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome evening sunshine
OL,14,Fdeveloping and staying mostly dry
OL,15,Fthrough the night, with plenty of
OL,16,Fclear spells across the region. Winds
OL,17,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
