OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA sunny day for most, with
OL,6,Flight winds. The risk of some coastal
OL,7,Fmist and fog moving across western
OL,8,FCornwall. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,12,Ffew days on Sunday and Monday, with
OL,13,Fplenty of warm spells of sunshine and
OL,14,Flight winds. Perhaps an increasing
OL,15,Fchance of showers developing later on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
